  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cashrooms is an interior design simulator where you can regularly <u>receive</u> items, <u>sell</u> and <u>trade</u> them on <strong>Steam</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every <u>one</u> hour you can<strong> get</strong> an <u>item</u> from one of the seven random category:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Common</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncommon</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rare</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Epic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Legendary</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Godlike</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Box</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Open</strong> <u>seasonal boxes</u> by purchasing <u>limited</u> items and making a collection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use</strong> items to design one of the available <u>32 rooms</u>. Collect them all and create a room of your dreams.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cashrooms is an interior design simulator where you can regularly <u>receive</u> items, <u>sell</u> and <u>trade</u> them on <strong>Steam</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every <u>one</u> hour you can<strong> get</strong> an <u>item</u> from one of the seven random category:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Common</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncommon</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rare</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Epic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Legendary</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Godlike</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Box</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Open</strong> <u>seasonal boxes</u> by purchasing <u>limited</u> items and making a collection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use</strong> items to design one of the available <u>32 rooms</u>. Collect them all and create a room of your dreams.</p>",
